Take a butter knife in

Take a tomato from the sofa
Keep the butter knife on the sofa
Take the tomato from the sofa

Wash the tomato in the sink

high_descs: Turn to left and walk into kitchen then find the sink.
Pick up the butter knife from the countertop.
Turn left, then straight until middle of coach, turn right and approach the sofa.
Slice up the tomato on the sofa.
Place the butter knife on the left side of the sofa.
Take a slice of the tomato.
Turn right then walk toward kitchen until reach the chair and turn left towards the sink.
Place the slice of tomato in the sink, rinse, then drain and remove.
Turn and walk around to the microwave.
Place the slice into the microwave and close the door.
anns.task_desc: Slice the tomato, rinse it and place into the microwave.

high_descs: Turn around and go near the sink.
Take the butter knife from the sink.
Turn around and go near the sofa.
Cut the tomato into pieces using the knife.
Put the butter knife on the sofa.
Take the piece of tomato from the sofa.
Turn around and go near the sink.
Put the tomato into the sink.
Then take it out and go near the microwave.
Put the tomato into the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Placed the piece of tomato into the microwave.
